<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Smoothie Menu </title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #4e342e;
        }
        header {
            background-color:  #6d4c41;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1em;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .menu-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color:  #795548;
            border-bottom: 2px solid  #6d4c41;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .menu-item {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;
        }
        .menu-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .menu-item h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #5d403;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .menu-item p {
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .price {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color:  #6d4c41;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        Smoothie Menu | Cafe
    </header>

    <div class="menu-container">

        <h2>Delicious Smoothies</h2>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Tropical Breeze Smoothie <span class="price">₹180</span></h3>
            <p>A refreshing blend of pineapple, mango, and coconut milk, creating a sweet, tropical flavor.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Berry Blast Smoothie <span class="price">₹200</span></h3>
            <p>A vibrant smoothie with strawberries, blueberries, raspberries, and orange juice, packed with antioxidants.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Green Power Smoothie <span class="price">₹220</span></h3>
            <p>A nutrient-packed blend of spinach, kale, green apple, banana, and almond milk for an energy boost.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Peanut Butter Banana Smoothie <span class="price">₹190</span></h3>
            <p>A creamy mix of bananas, peanut butter, honey, and almond milk, rich in protein.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Mango Madness Smoothie <span class="price">₹175</span></h3>
            <p>A tropical blend of mango, pineapple, and orange juice, creating a smooth and citrusy treat.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Avocado & Berry Smoothie <span class="price">₹250</span></h3>
            <p>A creamy, nutritious mix of avocado, mixed berries, and coconut water, rich in healthy fats.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Acai Bowl Smoothie <span class="price">₹260</span></h3>
            <p>A thick blend of acai berries, banana, granola, and almond milk, often topped with coconut flakes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Citrus Burst Smoothie <span class="price">₹180</span></h3>
            <p>A zesty smoothie with oranges, lemons, grapefruits, and a touch of ginger for a vitamin C boost.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Chocolate Protein Smoothie <span class="price">₹230</span></h3>
            <p>A rich blend of chocolate protein powder, banana, almond butter, and almond milk, great post-workout.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Carrot Cake Smoothie <span class="price">₹210</span></h3>
            <p>A blend of carrots, banana, cinnamon, ginger, and vanilla, bringing the flavors of carrot cake.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Apple Cinnamon Smoothie <span class="price">₹200</span></h3>
            <p>A cozy smoothie made with apples, banana, cinnamon, and oats, perfect for a comforting start.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Cucumber Mint Smoothie <span class="price">₹170</span></h3>
            <p>A light, refreshing mix of cucumber, mint, lime, and coconut water, perfect for hydration.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Strawberry Kiwi Smoothie <span class="price">₹190</span></h3>
            <p>A fruity blend of strawberries, kiwi, and orange juice, full of sweetness and vitamin C.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Pineapple Coconut Smoothie <span class="price">₹185</span></h3>
            <p>A tropical smoothie with pineapple, coconut milk, and banana, offering an island-like taste.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Peach & Oat Smoothie <span class="price">₹210</span></h3>
            <p>A smooth blend of peaches, oats, almond milk, and honey, perfect for a filling snack.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
